## Button Standards

### Primary Buttons
- Solid background with high contrast
- Minimum 44px height
- Clear hover/focus states
- Accessible via keyboard
- ARIA labels for screen readers

### Button States
- **Default**: Primary brand color
- **Hover**: Darker shade, cursor pointer
- **Focus**: Visible outline (2px)
- **Active**: Pressed state feedback
- **Disabled**: Reduced opacity, no interaction

### Code Example
```tsx
// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Accessible button
<button
  className="px-6 py-3 bg-[#E1BC56] text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-[#D4A94A] focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-2"
  aria-label="Submit booking"
>
  Book Now
</button>

// ‚ùå WRONG - No accessibility
<div onClick={handleClick}>Book</div>
```

