## Error Handling

### Error Display Standards
- Clear error messages
- Inline validation
- Helpful error recovery suggestions
- Accessible error announcements (`role="alert"`)

### Code Example
```tsx
// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Accessible error handling
{error && (
  <div role="alert" aria-live="polite" className="text-red-600">
    <p className="font-semibold">Error:</p>
    <p>{error.message}</p>
    <button onClick={handleRetry}>Try Again</button>
  </div>
)}
```

