- Visible focus indicators
- Escape key closes modals/dropdowns

### Screen Reader Support
- Semantic HTML elements
- ARIA labels where needed
- Descriptive alt text for images
- Proper heading hierarchy (h1 ‚Üí h2 ‚Üí h3)

### Code Example
